    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of the species Aesculus hippocastanum, white to pale yellowish-brown in color with a grain that is straight or spiral in pattern. It is used for furniture, turnery, and carving.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
